Package: mx-locale
Architecture: any
Depends: locales,
         xdg-utils | mx-viewer,
         ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Locale configuration tool for MX Linux
 MX Locale is a graphical utility that allows users to easily
 configure system language and locale settings. It provides
 a user-friendly interface for selecting and applying language
 preferences without requiring manual editing of configuration
 files or command line knowledge.
